WEBVTT

00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:13.930
WE LOVE STORIES
THAT TERRIFY US...

00:00:13.930 --> 00:00:19.030
STORIES THAT
ENCHANT US...

00:00:19.030 --> 00:00:24.960
STORIES THAT INSPIRE US...

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.630
AND WE ALWAYS HAVE.

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:30.660
THE POWER OF VISUAL
STORY-TELLING

00:00:30.660 --> 00:00:33.830
IS NOT A MODERN
PHENOMENON.

00:00:33.830 --> 00:00:37.660
FEATURE FILMS TODAY
ARE USING TECHNIQUES

00:00:37.660 --> 00:00:41.260
DEVELOPED WAY BACK
IN THE DISTANT PAST.

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:45.230
FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS ARTISTS
GRAPPLED WITH WAYS TO BRING

00:00:45.230 --> 00:00:50.660
THEIR STORIES ALIVE, TO
CAPTIVATE THEIR AUDIENCE.

00:00:50.660 --> 00:00:53.960
THIS IS THE STORY OF HOW
OUR ANCIENT ANCESTORS

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:57.430
MADE THE DISCOVERIES
THAT HAVE GIVEN FILM

00:00:57.430 --> 00:01:02.800
SUCH A HOLD OVER
OUR IMAGINATIONS.

