♪ HALLELUJAH, HALLELUJAH!
HALLELUJAH, HALLELUJAH, ♪

00:45:25.230 --> 00:45:27.830
♪ HALLELUJAH! ♪

00:45:27.830 --> 00:45:31.230
NOW RELIGIOUS STORYTELLERS
COULD USE THE CAPTIVATING

00:45:31.230 --> 00:45:33.230
POWER OF PICTURES
COMBINED WITH MUSIC

00:45:33.230 --> 00:45:37.300
TO REINFORCE THEIR
SPIRITUAL MESSAGE.

