♪ HALLELUJAH! ♪

00:45:49.200 --> 00:45:56.830
THEN IN 1894 A NEW VISUAL
STORYTELLING MEDIUM

00:45:56.830 --> 00:46:02.160
WAS INVENTED:
MOVING PICTURES.

00:46:02.160 --> 00:46:06.200
THIS IS THE FIRST
FEATURE FILM IN HISTORY.

00:46:06.200 --> 00:46:09.460
IT TOO COMES FROM AUSTRALIA
AND TELLS THE STORY

00:46:09.460 --> 00:46:12.030
OF THE OUTLAW
NED KELLY.

00:46:12.030 --> 00:46:16.130
HERE IS A HERO, A PLOT, AND
CHARACTERS WITH EMOTIONS.

00:46:16.130 --> 00:46:20.660
BUT IT LACKS THAT
CRUCIAL INGREDIENT.

00:46:20.660 --> 00:46:25.160
AS SOON AS FILMMAKERS
DISCOVERED HOW TO PUT

00:46:25.160 --> 00:46:32.730
SOUND INTO THEIR FILMS
CINEMA REALLY TOOK OFF.

00:46:32.730 --> 00:46:38.200
FINALLY DIRECTORS COULD
UNLOCK THE FULL POTENTIAL

00:46:38.200 --> 00:46:43.730
OF MOVING PICTURES.

00:46:43.730 --> 00:46:46.660
THEY'D FOUND A WAY TO
MOVE AN AUDIENCE SO MUCH

00:46:46.660 --> 00:46:49.200
THEY FELT AS THOUGH
THEY'D BEEN TRANSPORTED

00:46:49.200 --> 00:46:52.460
TO ANOTHER WORLD.

00:46:52.460 --> 00:46:56.860
ONE CANNOT UNDERESTIMATE
THE POWER OF SOUND EFFECTS

00:46:56.860 --> 00:47:00.360
AND MUSIC IN MODERN-DAY
FILMMAKING AND STORYTELLING.

00:47:00.360 --> 00:47:03.260
SO THAT WHEN YOU COME TO
SOMETHING LIKE LORENZO'S OIL

00:47:03.260 --> 00:47:07.260
WHERE WE HAVE A SCENE WHERE
THE PARENTS HAVING LEARNED OF

00:47:07.260 --> 00:47:11.160
THEIR TERRIBLE DIAGNOSIS
AND PROGNOSIS OF THEIR SON

00:47:11.160 --> 00:47:15.730
HAVE TO MAKE THE LONG WALK
OUT OF THE DOCTOR'S OFFICE.

00:47:15.730 --> 00:47:23.100
WE ENHANCED THEIR DEMEANOR,
THEIR MOOD, THEIR ANGUISH

00:47:23.100 --> 00:47:27.860
BY THE EXAGGERATED
SOUND OF THEIR FOOTSTEPS...

00:47:27.860 --> 00:47:32.800
BY THE LAUGHTER
OF A LITTLE GIRL...

00:47:32.800 --> 00:47:38.860
AND WITH THE MUSIC.

00:47:38.860 --> 00:47:41.830
THEY'RE HIDING THEIR
EMOTIONS BECAUSE THEY

00:47:41.830 --> 00:47:44.400
DON'T WANT THEIR SON TO
KNOW HOW THEY'RE FEELING

00:47:44.400 --> 00:47:50.460
AND YET THE MUSIC IS
TELLING US HOW THEY FEEL.

00:47:50.460 --> 00:47:56.560
WHEN WE GET HOME
CAN YOU READ A STORY?

00:47:56.560 --> 00:48:01.800
OF COURSE, MY DARLING.

00:48:01.800 --> 00:48:04.260
LET'S GO HOME.

