HAVE YOU EVER WONDERED WHY,
WHEN YOU'VE WATCHED A REALLY

00:48:18.030 --> 00:48:22.660
GOOD FILM, RATHER THAN LEAVE THE
CINEMA YOU STAY IN YOUR SEAT

00:48:22.660 --> 00:48:27.300
AND LISTEN TO THE MUSIC
PLAYING OVER THE END CREDITS?

00:48:27.300 --> 00:48:31.430
IT'S BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN
TRANSPORTED TO ANOTHER WORLD;

00:48:31.430 --> 00:48:34.560
AND ONCE THERE, YOU
CAN'T BEAR TO LEAVE.

00:48:34.560 --> 00:48:37.860
SO POWERFUL HAS
THAT EXPERIENCE BEEN,

00:48:37.860 --> 00:48:42.800
YOU JUST DON'T WANT
THE MAGIC TO END.

